author: bayard
msg: Applying patch from STR-3021. Thanks to Thomas Wilhelm for reporting the bug wherein exceptions thrown in tiles-included JSPs cause includes to happen twice. The change was to not consider an InvocationTargetException as a debug item, but as an exception whose contents need to be rethrown.
